column4: NSLOCTEXT("[A355802E48D1EBDF0BBCA2AAA8BA0AF7]", "2AF79A194B245EB24432A7BC4858670C", "Where are we? Is this a dream?")
NSLOCTEXT("[A355802E48D1EBDF0BBCA2AAA8BA0AF7]", "FE0F8A374F019A4B12DF358E932C6E79", "Calm down. My name is Frigimon. This is my house. I\'m an Ice Snow Digimon.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A355802E48D1EBDF0BBCA2AAA8BA0AF7]", "F50D47364BB72B82E5BAB5ADAC1A0531", "You were out cold in the snow. I picked you up and took care of you.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A355802E48D1EBDF0BBCA2AAA8BA0AF7]", "6563CB5241E61C9402352293F001B92D", "Hey, are you listening? If I didn\'t find you, you\'d be dead by now!")
NSLOCTEXT("[A355802E48D1EBDF0BBCA2AAA8BA0AF7]", "8D7C36FE4EEA1DC7FB9BA690C6482081", "Hey, {Partner}, I even hit my head when you suddenly fell down.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A355802E48D1EBDF0BBCA2AAA8BA0AF7]", "898A288E42CED5B78EBA4B8399B65C64", "{DigimonName} can\'t stand cold. You are so reckless. It\'s all your fault.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A355802E48D1EBDF0BBCA2AAA8BA0AF7]", "F447ECBF4443818B398422B59FF4BBA9", "Thanks, Frigimon. Can I ask you one more favor?")
NSLOCTEXT("[A355802E48D1EBDF0BBCA2AAA8BA0AF7]", "16F466B846228970C73D71A660C9F7A3", "What will you do if {DigimonName} falls down again? You\'d better go home soon!")
NSLOCTEXT("[A355802E48D1EBDF0BBCA2AAA8BA0AF7]", "F84294C14313A297DCD88589783EEFE0", "Alright, I got it. I\'ll digivolve {Partner} into another Digimon.")
